             Emirates NBD PJSC, the United Arab
Emiratesâ€™ biggest bank by assets, expects state-owned Dubai
World to reach an agreement on a debt restructuring plan by
September, Chief Executive Officer Rick Pudner said in a
conference call today.  
 Emirates NBD is one of the biggest lenders to Dubai World,
which is delaying repayment of $14.4 billion debt as part of a
restructuring plan.  
